name: Joshua
description: Truck driver for 1917 Logistics, a Co-Operative for truckers & logistics workers. he/they 🏴🚩
tweet:
My wife & I operated our own semi truck for 11 months in 2021 & generated over half a million dollars in revenue.

About 35% went to overhead expenses.

If we did the exact same work as employees, we'd have made ~$60k each & our boss would've kept $180k.

Capitalism is a scam.
